      "role": "user",
      "content": "I'm working on a color palette for a commercial law firm office. The goal is a \"calming yet professional\" atmosphere for the partner suites. Can you suggest a few muted blues and greys that would work well together? Please include the Hex codes for each.",
      "source": "evaluator"
